    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Alcohol. Action. Violence. Get ready to take your friends &quot;behind the sauna&quot;.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finnish Cabin Mayhem aims to provide an old school arcade shooter experience with a focus on chaotic melee combat. Use whatever there is at hand as a weapon to clubber your enemies in numerous different levels and game modes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alcohol infused multiplayer madness </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy various alcoholic beverages and beat the opposition with complex martial art techniques. Loot and utilize various improvised weapons such as sausages, baseball bats and pellet guns.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/64350d49fc5d3e62034aba03c04179a8.poster.avif?t=1748793969\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/64350d49fc5d3e62034aba03c04179a8.webm?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/64350d49fc5d3e62034aba03c04179a8.mp4?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High-octane action in multiple environments</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive bikes, plant mines, go to sauna and fire disposable rocket launchers. Gain access to ancient mythical weapons hidden in the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/268cf41ddf02f0a48f1a4325aa23fc2a.poster.avif?t=1748793969\" width=596 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/268cf41ddf02f0a48f1a4325aa23fc2a.webm?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/268cf41ddf02f0a48f1a4325aa23fc2a.mp4?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombie mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle for your life against an endless horde of zombies in a co-op zombie mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/d8999739a116b7b0fed60116009b631e.poster.avif?t=1748793969\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/d8999739a116b7b0fed60116009b631e.webm?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/d8999739a116b7b0fed60116009b631e.mp4?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character customization</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your character and unlock stylish apparel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/23987de5ab999ab809c6874ba721c75e.poster.avif?t=1748793969\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/23987de5ab999ab809c6874ba721c75e.webm?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/23987de5ab999ab809c6874ba721c75e.mp4?t=1748793969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
